OL,3,CMan deemed 'significant risk to
OL,4,Celderly women' jailed
OL,6,FA man from Wiltshire who posed a
OL,7,F"significant risk to elderly women"
OL,8,Fhas been jailed after threatening a
OL,9,Fhomeowner with a knife.
OL,11,FGeorge Gale forced his way into the
OL,12,Fvictim's house on August 12 2024 and
OL,13,Fdemanded money and jewellery.
OL,15,FThe 27-year-old, of Doveys Terrace,
OL,16,Ftold his victim - a woman in her 70s -
OL,17,Fhe would kill her and her pets if she
OL,18,Fcalled for help.
