OL,3,CMan deemed 'significant risk to
OL,4,Celderly women' jailed
OL,6,FDuring sentencing at Swindon Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Monday 17 February, Judge
OL,8,FTaylor described Gale as a
OL,9,F"significant risk" especially to
OL,10,F"elderly women".
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to 14 years in prison
OL,13,F- of which he must serve at least two
OL,14,Fthirds - and issued with an indefinite
OL,15,Frestraining order not to contact his
OL,16,Fvictim or enter Kington Langley.
