OL,6,FDetective Constable Tom Carver, from
OL,7,FWiltshire Police's CID team, said: "I
OL,8,Fwant to thank Gale's victim who has
OL,9,Fshown incredible bravery throughout
OL,10,Fthe judicial process.
OL,12,F"On that night in August, he
OL,13,Ffrightened her so much that she did
OL,14,Fnot want to tell the police, and it
OL,15,Fwas only when a friend reported it to
OL,16,Fus did she reveal what had happened.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
